{"tid":1888617,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳志雲嘲鄧炳強冇腦","createTime":"2020-02-20T10:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T10:00:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"358d1fb051b7d5ddc6ef55ec285a6fee5c701e76","tid":1888617,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:00:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200220/6WSAHPWANHQTP2NEAZFUZYMCNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200220%2F6WSAHPWANHQTP2NEAZFUZYMCNE%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=8140dbff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200220%2F6WSAHPWANHQTP2NEAZFUZYMCNE%2F&h=5e0c5735\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200220/6WSAHPWANHQTP2NEAZFUZYMCNE/</a><br />\n<br />\n陳志雲嘲鄧炳強冇腦<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長鄧炳強與明星的無罩宴廣受非議，陳志雲昨早在商台《在晴朗的一天出發》中狠批是壞榜樣：「一個咁高級嘅紀律部隊阿頭，竟然咁冇common sense，喺政府大力宣傳減少社交聚會嘅時候做呢啲嘢。」影片中見到飯局有人在室內吸煙，陳志雲炮轟：「大庭廣眾喺度食煙簡直係違法，結論係，第一佢（鄧炳強）唔記得帶自己個腦出街；第二，更有可能嘅就係呢個處長係冇腦嘅。一個咁嘅社交聚會，會冇人拍低或錄低？警覺意識咁嘅話，點可以期望香港警隊係專業。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：舒琪諷朱經緯害全家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200220/large/1582118717_d5c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582118717_d5c8.jpg&h=2f25215e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳志雲昨日開咪炮轟鄧炳強沒有常識，又嘲他冇腦，警覺意識低。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲更謂︰「呢啲行為令市民失望，直情係令政府蒙羞。」鄧炳強說跟成龍等人學做警察，陳志雲直言：「好學唔學，警察最忌係乜？英雄主義。成龍嘅電影最標榜英雄主義。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：曹家誠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200220/large/1582118716_8bd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582118716_8bd1.jpg&h=a0f15ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，但成龍等與警察飯局依然沒戴口罩。互聯網圖片"}]}